# ===== NODEMAILER EMAIL CONFIGURATION =====
GMAIL_EMAIL=your-gmail@gmail.com
GMAIL_APP_PASSWORD=your-16-character-app-password
SMTP_HOST=smtp.gmail.com
SMTP_PORT=587
RECIPIENT_EMAIL=your-business-email@company.com


# ===== CONFIGURATION NOTES =====
# Gmail App Password: Get from Google Account > Security > App passwords
# Form submissions will be sent TO: RECIPIENT_EMAIL (where you want to receive leads)
# Form submissions will be sent FROM: GMAIL_EMAIL (your Gmail account)
# User thank you emails will be sent FROM: GMAIL_EMAIL TO: User's submitted email

# ===== SETUP INSTRUCTIONS =====
# 1. Enable 2-Factor Authentication in your Google Account
# 2. Go to Google Account Settings > Security > App passwords
# 3. Generate an app password for "Mail"
# 4. Use the 16-character password (remove spaces) in GMAIL_APP_PASSWORD
# 5. Replace GMAIL_EMAIL with your Gmail address
# 6. Replace RECIPIENT_EMAIL with where you want to receive form submissions
# 7. Copy this file to .env.local and update with your actual values

